articles.title: „Man muss die Keime des ausgelebten Judenhasses ersticken“
articles.image_title: April 8, 2023, Berlin, Germany: Today, on April 8, 2023, in Berlin, protesters gathered at city hall Neukoelln to demonstrate against the 2023 Al-Aqsa clashes. These violent confrontations occurred between Palestinian worshippers and Israeli police at the Al-Aqsa Mosque in Jerusalem. Palestinian groups have condemned the attacks, while Israeli authorities have defended their actions as necessary for maintaining public order and safety.
